metadata.name: task was to train a core group
metadata.description:
effectively manage the people, increase the output of rice, harvest the heaven and earth, and strengthen the war skills.



Cultivating them will not delay their own cultivation breakthrough?



Don't.



Because it's not that the more time you spend in seclusion, the better. But there is a point, the so-called golden mean, too much of a good thing. Too long a period of practice may harm the meridians and spiritual acupoints and backfire.



It's the same with physical exercise.
